ollower 急升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"Ig呢"},{"pid":"d800fc182e00d4c370db37834b7e4b60556546e9","tid":788410,"uid":73112,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"呢啲成日誘惑人既賤女人一定要好好教訓下<br />\n起勢咁聞佢對大肉腳啲香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再含佢腳趾舔佢腳板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好就一一邊踩住我臉一邊囂張咁屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用碌鳩頂佢腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大屁股，淫奶同格肋底又滑又香 質個頭入去索 舔到佢啲淫肉全部都係口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用佢對肉腳同大臀肉打我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩臀交奶交腋交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪賤女人成日咁囂張喺咪成日故意突對奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cca6ba6285d554559be489731a6d0b495fac9d","tid":788410,"uid":194308,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"ci